Node:	near_or_far (Spoken declaration of whether or not something is nearby)
Input:
	None
Config: 
	from srv_sonar:
		proximity < 100cm 	"Near" 
					o/w 	"Far"
Output:
	String near_far ["Near", "Far"]
Steps:
	1. Initialization: request proximity from srv_sonar
	2. if proximity is >= to 100cm then:
		(a) near_far = "Far"
		(b) send request to srv_speaker (near_far)
	3. else
		(a) near_far = "Near"
		(b) send request to srv_speaker (near_far)
